1
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:21,320
Mo Di is dead.

2
00:00:21,680 --> 00:00:23,000
From now on,

3
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:25,320
I am your new master.

4
00:00:28,840 --> 00:00:30,160
Yes, Master.

5
00:00:34,440 --> 00:00:35,400
A'yu.

6
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:41,680
Didn't we agree to return to the Yuyun tree together?

7
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,640
A'yu.

8
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,800
Move a bit to the side. Good.

9
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,200
Okay, good.

10
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:23,640
Okay.

11
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,370
Coming down.

12
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:26,520
I brought it.

13
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,520
Move these two inside.

14
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:34,280
Alright.

15
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,200
Make way.

16
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,720
Jiuyun.

17
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,570
I've waited ten years for this day.

18
00:01:58,479 --> 00:02:00,160
At such an important time,

19
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,130
do you have to be so serious?

20
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,920
They just want to keep you safe.

21
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:08,000
Forcing me to marry you like this,

22
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,840
what's the point?

23
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,320
Jiuyun.

24
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,600
Let's drink the nuptial wine first.

25
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,840
A'yu.

26
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,440
I know you're here.

27
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,160
Come out.

28
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:12,770
Are you just going to watch me marry someone else?

29
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:15,360
Come out quickly. I know you're here.

30
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,210
Since you don't want to,

31
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,040
then don't marry him.

32
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,720
I knew you would show up.

33
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,810
Since you're already here,

34
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,480
just sit for a while.

35
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:03,960
Ayu, why did you leave without saying goodbye?

36
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,400
I wrote everything

37
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,760
I wanted to say in the letter.

38
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,480
I don't believe a word in that letter.

39
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,160
I can feel

40
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,640
that you've been by my side.

41
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:17,640
Yun,

42
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,160
I just want you to be happy.

43
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:23,440
Being with you is the happiness I want.

44
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,680
Yun.

45
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,320
I actually just...

46
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:29,400
Jiuyun is already my wife.

47
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,840
You'd better behave.

48
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:35,040
Su Cheng, let Mo Yu go.

49
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,920
I promise I won't run away again.

50
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,400
It's not me who won't let him go.

51
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,440
It's you.

52
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:43,400
From the moment you used me to force Mo Yu to appear,

53
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:46,060
you should have known I wouldn't show any mercy.

54
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,240
If A'yu dies,

55
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,320
I won't live without him.

56
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,040
Whether you live or die

57
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,240
has nothing to do with me.

58
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,920
But as long as you meet one condition,

59
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,880
I will let him go.

60
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,200
What condition?

61
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,720
Hand over the Dandian

62
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,970
and help me restore my kingdom.

63
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,320
A'yun, don't agree to it.

64
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,520
If you don't write it,

65
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,640
you can collect his corpse.

66
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:29,960
No.

67
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,720
I'll write it.

68
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,080
Lian

69
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,880
shan

70
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,240
lu

71
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,080
zang

72
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,080
gu.

73
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:05,760
Lianshanlu, Guizanggu.

74
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,960
The Pill Manual is finished.

75
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,400
You should let her go.

76
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:18,840
Su Cheng.

77
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,920
What are you doing?

78
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:26,920
What do you mean?

79
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:32,200
I promised not to kill you,

80
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,880
but I didn't promise not to kill her.

81
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,040
What exactly do you want?

82
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:39,080
What I want is simple.

83
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:42,400
Go to the treasure site and get the treasure for me.

84
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,760
Don't agree to it.

85
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:48,400
He just wants you to risk your life.

86
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,720
But I can't let you get hurt.

87
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,200
Ayun.

88
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,080
My days are already numbered.

89
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,480
Let me go.

90
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,800
In the final moments of my life,

91
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,600
exchanging my life

92
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,160
for yours,

93
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,060
leaves me with no regrets.

94
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,800
Cut the crap.

95
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,400
Go right now.

96
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:31,480
Baorui.

97
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:31,680
Bo.

98
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,850
Zijian Qiangqipin.

99
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,400
Quan Xuhang.

100
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,330
Kun Quan Xuhang.

101
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,409
Quan Yulong.

102
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,860
Licheng Lefei.

103
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:42,600
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing.

104
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,260
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing.

105
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:46,760
Luoxiao Conglin Xunbo.

106
